  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/611690/extras/abb4c0a3b51069c12a862495642c0167.avif?t=1735729588\" width=616 height=98 /></span><br>Your early memories of playing action games on your game console have been a defining moment of your childhood. In the years that passed you have kept those memories as ones of the dearest to you.<br><br>However, there was always that feeling of unfinished business about a series of cartridges you could never beat as a kid. One day, cleaning your old place you have found them again. It’s almost like they have called you. A stack of cartridges with a name you remember well…<br><br>Shoot your way through droids, mini-bosses, Threehorn’s arena and meet Deacon’s alter ego.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/611690/extras/fbbac18764bee80ea9f99c64fd320e3d.avif?t=1735729588\" width=616 height=98 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fast-paced FPS<br></li><li>Two unique bosses<br></li><li>Bonus game between the levels<br></li><li>Powerful weapon with three fire modes and shield generator<br></li><li>Physics based plasma bullets with a twist<br></li><li>Perk cartridges<br></li><li>High end graphics and visual effects<br></li><li>Carefully crafted game feel, presentation and soundtrack</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/611690/extras/5551325026f636f435e22451ada8bb4a.poster.avif?t=1735729588\" width=616 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/611690/extras/5551325026f636f435e22451ada8bb4a.webm?t=1735729588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/611690/extras/5551325026f636f435e22451ada8bb4a.mp4?t=1735729588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/611690/extras/abb4c0a3b51069c12a862495642c0167.avif?t=1735729588\" width=616 height=98 /></span><br>Your early memories of playing action games on your game console have been a defining moment of your childhood. In the years that passed you have kept those memories as ones of the dearest to you.<br><br>However, there was always that feeling of unfinished business about a series of cartridges you could never beat as a kid. One day, cleaning your old place you have found them again. It’s almost like they have called you. A stack of cartridges with a name you remember well…<br><br>Shoot your way through droids, mini-bosses, Threehorn’s arena and meet Deacon’s alter ego.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/611690/extras/fbbac18764bee80ea9f99c64fd320e3d.avif?t=1735729588\" width=616 height=98 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fast-paced FPS<br></li><li>Two unique bosses<br></li><li>Bonus game between the levels<br></li><li>Powerful weapon with three fire modes and shield generator<br></li><li>Physics based plasma bullets with a twist<br></li><li>Perk cartridges<br></li><li>High end graphics and visual effects<br></li><li>Carefully crafted game feel, presentation and soundtrack</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/611690/extras/5551325026f636f435e22451ada8bb4a.poster.avif?t=1735729588\" width=616 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/611690/extras/5551325026f636f435e22451ada8bb4a.webm?t=1735729588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/611690/extras/5551325026f636f435e22451ada